# Dashboard Walkthrough

## Dashboard 1: Ops Overview (Executive)
Widgets:
- Open Incidents by Priority
- Incidents Trend (Created)
- Incidents Trend (Resolved)
- Changes by State
- Problems by Known Error
- Top Assignment Groups – Open Incidents

Purpose:
Provides leadership a quick operational snapshot and highlights workload, risk areas, and trends.

## Dashboard 2: Service Desk Daily (Team)
Widgets:
- Open Incidents by Assignment Group
- Incidents Created vs Resolved (trend comparison)
- Top priorities open today
- (Optional) My group’s open incidents using interactive filters

Purpose:
Helps service desk teams manage day-to-day queues and identify backlogs.
